headline: Accenture Expands AI Ecosystem With Mistral AI As Shares Trade Lower
summary: Accenture (NYSE:ACN) has entered a multi-year collaboration with Mistral AI to co-develop enterprise-grade AI solutions. The agreement also includes training and certification programs to help clients adopt and govern AI responsibly.
